OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FAny early
OL,6,Fevening showers pushing southwards and
OL,7,Fsoon fading to leave a generally dry
OL,8,Fnight, although remaining rather
OL,9,Fcloudy. Winds easing and turning
OL,10,Frather cool in the north.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSunday:FSunday will be a dry day with
OL,13,Flight winds and a mix of fair weather
OL,14,Fcloud and bright or sunny spells.
OL,15,FFeeling warmer for all in the sunshine.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
