OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FDry
OL,6,Fwith sunny spells on Monday. Becoming
OL,7,Fmore unsettled from Tuesday with rain
OL,8,For showers at times, turning windier,
OL,9,Fespecially by Wednesday. Remaining
OL,10,Frather warm throughout.
